title: On The Run Sugar Baby or *STRANGE* Coincidences?
description:
Hi friends, how are you today? I hope you are having a wonderful day so far! I have really been enjoying these stories from long ago, the women sure were a little cray, to say the least. But I must say, there were a lot of strange coincidences going on around Louise's life, wasn't there? She was the definition of suspish to say the least. Thank you for tuning into Murder, Mystery & Makeup. I love and appreciate you so much, and I hope to be seeing you very soon.
xo
